				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Each class has disadvantages in pvp, its how you learn to cope with what you can and cant do that will make the difference.
<br />
It's all about taking your weaknesses and turning them into strengths, if you read Graffes wiz board you will find Wizzies complaining that mages have to much nuke power combined with pets. Personally i dont agree (we are elementalists who can only cast 2 spheres of elements, air/fire give us water and earth and i'm a happy chappie <img src="images/smiles/icon_wink.gif" alt="wink" border="0" /> ).
<br />
Its all in how your play and what you are looking for, i am a 65 mage on SZ, and i can hold my own, though from 46+ (pop planes) most pvp is not 1 vs 1 its 5+ vs 5+ and in that type of fight we are dangerous, pet on 1 enemy nuking another pet burn on caster etc etc. 
<br />
Ours is a diverse role which i am glad to have taken.
