				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I play on a real pvp =0 rellos zek where most people dont wear dropable gear, no offense you to the other people. But i know on rellos alot of people arent fully geared 50% o the time or in the late 40's and so on have all no drop, as if you look at my profile i dont even wear full gear. I got every thing to get my resist to 200+ but disease and poison but just incase that one pker comes i dont wear it, Gear is a big thing thats what i was trying to point out.
<br />

<br />
Second killing a cleric is either a 20 sec job, or a long ass fight.
<br />

<br />
This is how i usually starta pvp fight out that i know im about to fight, mem your best friend annul magic. or the lesser counter part if your not that lvl yet. Most people put bigger, hp buffs and such after sow and gimp stuff. So first thing i try to do when i fight a cleric type is cancle there sow, this gives you the great advanatage of being able to kite them incase they have good melee skills. If you got the surprise on them, hell toss anull two times on them, most of the time they wont be paying attention and result here goes there hps buffs most of the time and what ever else.  Use earth pet for clerics, or air if there isnt a zone near by &lt;I cant stand people runing from me&gt;. Since a cleric isnt all good in the nuking department for a while toss a something from the malise line, for me it would be malo. Then just nuke away and try to to stop there healing, at this point its either they are healing 24/7 or trying to gate, or your dead already because he had a friend &lt;Never loose to a cleric, its a shameful thing to do, almost as bad as loosing to a warrior&gt;.
<br />

<br />
Thats my general way of kiling a cleric, annul is my best friend and should be yours, Just make sure you line your buffs up right incase u get rooted you can just cast cancle magic or your choice of spell.
<br />

<br />
As for you gear, get easy magic resist, thats all clerics would toss on you.
<br />

<br />
&lt;Just be happy clerics cant lay hands&gt;
<br />

<br />

<br />
Also I'm not a pker, im pure anti if any thing. I just hunt down/help alot of people who are geting CC'ed and such. Its fun and keeps the game interesting, i would never go back to a blue server.
<br />

<br />
Also wanted to add one thing, clerics are good pkers, if they are geared right and if they are with people &lt;A bitch to kill a cleric and a tank class&gt;. But just get MR above 200 or hell 250 and you will fly by them.
<br />

<br />
Peace.
<br />

<br />
PS: Dont go to TZ boring there, no chance of loot from pkers and such, you got lvl 14 twinks prolly owning up CB or other newb zones, on RZ atleast you got the antis and pks there and its so goddamn funny when the pks loose a fungi or ikky..... It just makes it more interesting and tactful when playing, to wear gear or not to wear gear.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=742948" target="_blank" class="postlink">Ghetoman Totherescue's Gear</a>
<br />
Rellos Zek - PVP
